title: Political Dialogue without Nuking Relationships (Live Speech)
description:
This is my first Toastmasters speech, recorded on 11/14/23 at Beacon Toastmasters club. 

Overall, I thought it went well. Here are a few pieces of constructive feedback I received: 

- work on eliminating filler words: um, like, and, so, etc. 
- integrate humor, especially at the beginning of the speech
- during the flat earth and dueling illustrations, I should have paused more to let them sink in
